@startuml
title Sequence Diagram for Notification Sending

actor User
participant NotificationAPI
participant NotificationManager
participant NotificationDB

User -> NotificationAPI: sendNotification(userId, message)
NotificationAPI -> NotificationManager: createNotification(userId, message)
NotificationManager -> NotificationDB: saveNotification(notification)
NotificationDB --> NotificationManager: acknowledge save
NotificationManager -> NotificationAPI: notificationSent
NotificationAPI --> User: return success
@enduml
